<text top="694" left="313" width="241" height="9" font="font16" id="p1_t52" reading_order_no="58" segment_no="21" tag_type="text">This study describes the physical characteristics of salt</text>
<text top="705" left="313" width="241" height="9" font="font16" id="p1_t53" reading_order_no="59" segment_no="21" tag_type="text">ponds in the British Virgin Islands (BVI), a small archipel-</text>
